# Local Risk Alert Feed (framework) — Environment Variables
#
# The framework itself needs no API keys. Plugin-specific secrets (Ticketmaster,
# AirNow, Georgia 511, TRANSCOM, etc.) live with the plugins in the consuming
# repo, and federated-plugin credentials are resolved at runtime via a
# CredentialResolver (see architecture/plugin-federation.md).
#
# Convention for federated plugin credentials (EnvCredentialResolver):
#   PLUGIN_<ID>_TOKEN=...
#   PLUGIN_<ID>_SIGNING_SECRET=...
#   PLUGIN_<ID>_TOKEN_PREVIOUS=...          # optional, during rotation
#   PLUGIN_<ID>_SIGNING_SECRET_PREVIOUS=... # optional, during rotation
